---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const pageTitle = "CalorieBot FAQ - Frequently Asked Questions";
const pageDescription = "Find answers to common questions about CalorieBot Discord fitness bot, features, pricing, setup, and affiliate commissions.";
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative bg-dark text-white py-8 md:py-12 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-48 bg-orange-600/5 blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-1/3 h-48 bg-discord/5 blur-3xl"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-center relative">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
            <span class="inline-block">Frequently Asked</span>
            <span class="text-orange-500 inline-block">Questions</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl mb-8 text-gray-300">
            Everything you need to know about CalorieBot, from setup to features and monetization.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Sections -->
    <section class="py-12 md:py-20 bg-secondary">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

        <!-- Getting Started FAQ -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8 text-center">Getting Started</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">How do I add CalorieBot to my Discord server?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Click the "Add CalorieBot" button on our homepage, select your server, and authorize the required permissions.
                You'll need administrator permissions to add bots to your server.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">What permissions does CalorieBot need?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                CalorieBot requires permissions to send messages, embed links, attach files, use slash commands, and manage channels for setup.
                These permissions are automatically requested during the authorization process.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">Is there a free trial?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Yes! CalorieBot offers a 7-day free trial for up to 5 members. No credit card is required to start.
                After the trial, users can subscribe for $19.99/month to continue using all features.
              </p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Features FAQ -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8 text-center">Features</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">How accurate is the AI photo calorie tracking?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Our AI technology provides highly accurate calorie estimates by analyzing food items, portions, and preparation methods.
                Users can fine-tune entries with our adjustment feature for even greater precision.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">Can I customize workouts for my equipment?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Absolutely! CalorieBot's AI workout builder adapts to your available equipment, fitness goals, and time constraints.
                Whether you have a full gym, home equipment, or just bodyweight, we'll create the perfect workout.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">How do weekly challenges work?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Weekly challenges automatically track your nutrition and workout data, setting daily targets for calories, workouts, steps, and protein.
                If you miss a target, you can complete redemption challenges to stay in the competition.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">Can I track progress photos?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Yes! CalorieBot includes progress photo tracking to help you visualize your fitness journey.
                You can upload photos and track changes over time alongside your nutrition and workout data.
              </p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pricing & Monetization FAQ -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8 text-center">Pricing & Monetization</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">How much does CalorieBot cost?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                CalorieBot costs $19.99/month per user. This includes all features: AI photo tracking, guided workouts,
                challenges, social sharing, and progress analytics. There's no additional cost for server admins.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">How do affiliate commissions work?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Server admins earn 60% commission ($12/month) for every user who subscribes in their server.
                We keep 40% ($7.99/month) to cover platform costs. Commissions are paid automatically through Stripe.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">How do I set up affiliate payments?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Connect your Stripe account through our affiliate setup process. Once connected, you'll automatically
                receive 60% commission on every user subscription in your server. No additional setup required.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">When do I get paid?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Commissions are paid monthly through Stripe, typically within 2-7 days after the end of each month.
                You can track your earnings and subscriber count in real-time through your admin dashboard.
              </p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Technical FAQ -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8 text-center">Technical</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">Is my data secure?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Yes, we take data security seriously. All data is encrypted in transit and at rest.
                We comply with privacy regulations and never share your personal information with third parties.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">Can I export my data?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Yes, you can export your food logs, workout data, and progress information at any time.
                Use the /export command to download your data in a convenient format.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">What if I have technical issues?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Our support team is here to help! You can reach us through Discord, email, or our support channels.
                We typically respond within 24 hours and are committed to resolving any issues quickly.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-3">Can I use CalorieBot on mobile?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                CalorieBot works perfectly on mobile devices through the Discord mobile app.
                All features including photo uploads, workouts, and challenges are fully supported on mobile.
              </p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-12 md:py-20 bg-dark">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Still Have Questions?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Can't find what you're looking for? Contact our support team for personalized help.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="https://discord.com/api/oauth2/authorize?client_id=123456789&permissions=395137251392&scope=bot%20applications.commands"
            class="inline-block bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-500 text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full transition-colors text-lg"
          >
            Add CalorieBot Free
          </a>
          <a
            href="/user-guide/"
            class="inline-block bg-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-500 text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full transition-colors text-lg"
          >
            View User Guide
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
